{"tid":772071,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"傻鳩 你估ocamp真係咁多人扑野咩 你班中學青頭雞","createTime":"2018-08-08T12:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T02:17:05.000Z","uid":54581,"like":7,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"69466c8a729367223d7772f2cab4f787afd11b8d","tid":772071,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"Ocamp頂盡抽下水<br />\n<br />\n玩水game濕身騎膊頭就一定啦<br />\n想當年呀叔我俾個漏m既女一騎 hi到啲m血就行足三年衰運<br />\n<br />\n番正題，<br />\n玩房game就最多摸下手仔大脾，玩激啲就錫下臉咁<br />\n<br />\n不過呢，就多數男同男玩<br />\n<br />\n所以條女玩ocamp無咩大不了～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最攞命係啲reu, 通k 酒game<br />\n<br />\n我個時都係靠reu 溝到個組女上床～<br />\n佢同佢條仔拍左三年拖 西都未摸過就俾我開左疱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再講 ocamp玩左幾年 聽過幾間u<br />\n<br />\n仲係得幾個fm係ocamp個陣俾人食左<br />\n<br />\n正常一大班人 唔見左個女fm 係好撚奇怪的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話組爸媽自己偷間房扑野就大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ebb1ecf8e7e7804f43d45b35d14c3d6c2b6e03","tid":772071,"uid":94828,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"祝你以後識親女都戴綠帽"},{"pid":"08a9f077a4488e15a945cb23facdcea8dfd11c13","tid":772071,"uid":54581,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"c9ebb1ecf8e7e7804f43d45b35d14c3d6c2b6e03","tid":772071,"uid":94828,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:49:29.000Z","msg":"祝你以後識親女都戴綠帽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"我都幫你帶左幾頂啦老襟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8735665b4eb55d66151b04d405051174f5eca1","tid":772071,"uid":69761,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"岩岩扑左"},{"pid":"90dbe19273de7061e24f5ad75cd4d0026a3d9e7a","tid":772071,"uid":54581,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T12:51:22.000Z","msg":"Btw 條女係俾第個狗公搞散左我先入手<br />\n<br />\n原來佢一路對我有好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=